<li><a href="http://www.dnatechindia.com/index.php/Tutorials/8051-Tutorial/Switch-Interfacing.html" class="external text" title="http://www.dnatechindia.com/index.php/Tutorials/8051-Tutorial/Switch-Interfacing.html" rel="nofollow">Interfacing switch to 8051 Controller</a></li>
</ul>


